---
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4 bg-yellow-100 text-primary">
        Nossas Vantagens
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Por Que Confiar na MM Entulho?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Legalidade, responsabilidade ambiental e transparência total em cada serviço
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      {/* Diferencial 1 - Autorizado pelo SLU */}
      <div class="flex gap-5 md:gap-6 group">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 md:h-20 md:w-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-700 text-white shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 md:h-10 md:w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm3.5-9c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S16.33 8 15.5 8 14 8.67 14 9.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm-7 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S9.33 8 8.5 8 7 8.67 7 9.5 7.67 11 8.5 11zm3.5 6.5c2.33 0 4.31-1.46 5.11-3.5H6.89c.8 2.04 2.78 3.5 5.11 3.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Autorizado pelo SLU
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Somos autorizados pela Secretaria de Limpeza Urbana do Distrito Federal. Coleta e destinação legal e responsável.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Diferencial 2 - Descarte Consciente */}
      <div class="flex gap-5 md:gap-6 group">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 md:h-20 md:w-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-700 text-white shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 md:h-10 md:w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm-1-5h2v2h-2zm0-10h2v10h-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Descarte Consciente
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Todo resíduo é destinado a aterros licenciados. Cuidamos do meio ambiente em cada coleta de entulho em Brasília.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Diferencial 3 - Caçambas Rastreadas */}
      <div class="flex gap-5 md:gap-6 group">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 md:h-20 md:w-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-700 text-white shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 md:h-10 md:w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Caçambas Rastreadas
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Acompanhe em tempo real o seu entulho. Transparência total sobre coleta, transporte e destinação.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Diferencial 4 - CTR */}
      <div class="flex gap-5 md:gap-6 group">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 md:h-20 md:w-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-700 text-white shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 md:h-10 md:w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm3.5-9c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S16.33 8 15.5 8 14 8.67 14 9.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm-7 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S9.33 8 8.5 8 7 8.67 7 9.5 7.67 11 8.5 11zm3.5 6.5c2.33 0 4.31-1.46 5.11-3.5H6.89c.8 2.04 2.78 3.5 5.11 3.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Controle de Transporte (CTR)
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Comprovante oficial de destinação incluído. Você tem certeza de que seu entulho foi descartado corretamente.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
